SYSTEM: A millenia ago, the great city of Mahrjestrom incurred the wrath of the gods and was destroyed. Its sudden reappearance ten days ago was an augur of ill fortune, for soon after, a madness took the villagers and nomads of the remote north. Those who would seek their fortune in the lost City of the Unquenchable Sky are few and far between, and those willing to risk madness for fame and fortune are rarer still.\nBut HERO-FULL, IDIOT-FULL, and SNARKY-FULL set out for glory again, guided by SECOND-FULL, and if they're lucky -- or perhaps unlucky -- they may just find what frightened the gods enough to destroy the city...